                     <join result="offenceCrimeDate" targOrder="Y" targets="t17930109-47-off252 t17930109-47-cd253"></join>, a pair of linen sheets, value 4 s. and a flat iron, value 8 d. the goods of 
                     
                        <persName id="t17930109-47-victim484" type="victimName">
