                  </persName>
             pledged the sheets on the 7th of December one pair of sheets; she had fetched the sheets and blankets out often; I have the sheets here. (Deposed to by the prosecutor.)</p>
               <p>
            
                  <persName id="t17930109-47-person489">
                  JOHN
                   KEEP
               <interp inst="t17930109-47-person489" type="surname" value="KEEP"></interp>
